e\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"f4e185e9-5306-1d65-9b76-7fac6e1237c7","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"567c970c-8c14-7d04-ece3-f150af1c9621","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"30308302-aa2c-0b01-5928-01aa82e9b474","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Load Previous Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"815774e9-a167-354c-745f-05cf649c7b99","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"befef745-6efd-5a61-83e5-074cd124e967","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"7385a22c-bb94-4c63-c782-d30b35c25bb1","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Airtable)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,520],"id":"b305b8ca-16af-3987-2fd3-78746a4909a4","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Airtable)\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,520],"id":"5cd52ccf-50e2-5381-115b-6885c75c25af","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Airtable)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,520],"id":"27f9a3c4-7023-371a-2b9d-e316381a5a92","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,1540],"id":"248e7b33-fd99-8468-6764-d9c5a82b46a3","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,1540],"id":"742ed665-feec-f4c7-e941-9576ac55f24d","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,1540],"id":"24cfcbe9-dbbe-d5ae-7985-a7f337a32c09","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Nurture trial users with Airtable and Microsoft Teams automatically\n\n**Pattern:** Drip Sequence · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nNurture trial users with Airtable and Microsoft Teams automatically. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual auto-responders is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Stamp & Shape Email → Payload Valid? → Score the Lead → Assign Round-Robin Owner → Route by Heat → Hot → Airtable + Instant Ping → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to drip sequence without manual effort\n- Anyone automating auto-responders in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; Google OAuth2 / service account; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"ad42fd7c-1f1c-a04e-3161-ff0b186cfc9e","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"91b1a3c3-7003-d6e7-ea1e-70b4f68af2a1","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your auto-responders process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"1eca786e-59f4-b918-392f-4ae96d070c78","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Daily Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Email":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Score the Lead","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Score the Lead":{"main":[[{"node":"Assign Round-Robin Owner","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Assign Round-Robin Owner":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Heat","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hot → Airtable + Instant Ping":{"main":[[{"node":"Notify Assigned Owner","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Heat":{"main":[[{"node":"Hot → Airtable + Instant Ping","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Warm → Drip via Microsoft Teams","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Cold → Park in Nurture List","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Notify Assigned Owner":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Warm → Drip via Microsoft Teams":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cold → Park in Nurture List":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Combine Lead Paths":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Airtable)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Airtable)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"0a0aaf25-37e6-4d4f-9896-4ae448db613c","id":"FDX02370"}